Class CountryModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thedomination.model.CountryModel

  • public class CountryModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The CountryModel Class. Initializes countryName String, a ContinentModel ContinentModel as belongsTo and a ArrayList ArrayList as listofNewNeighbours. Initializes countryPosition as Integer.
